<P>THE <HI>Ca&s;tle of Andalu&s;ia,</HI> A COMIC OPERA.</P>
<P>IN THREE ACTS.</P>
<P>AS IT IS PERFORMED At the THEATRES in LONDON And DUBLIN.</P>
<P>By JOHN O'KEEFE, E&s;qr.</P>
<P>SOLD BY THE BOOKSELLERS.</P>
<P>M, DCC, LXXXIII.</P>
</DIV1>
